<section class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4">🛡️ Privacy Policy – NotiK</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> May 14, 2025</p>

    <p>At NotiK, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting the personal information you provide to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data when you access our website and use our services.</p>

    <h5 class="mt-4">1. Who are we?</h5>
    <p>We are NotiK, a service that provides economic alerts sent directly to your WhatsApp. Our website is: <em>www.notik.com</em>.</p>

    <h5 class="mt-4">2. Data we collect</h5>
    <p>When you register or interact with our website, we may collect the following information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Username or name</li>
        <li>Phone number (for WhatsApp alerts).</li>
        <li>Email address.</li>
        <li>IP address, browser type, and other technical data.</li>
        <li>Browsing information through cookies.</li>
    </ul>

    <h5 class="mt-4">3. How do we use your data?</h5>
    <p>We use your data to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Send notifications about relevant economic events.</li>
        <li>Manage your account and preferences.</li>
        <li>Improve our services and user experience.</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations.</li>
    </ul>

    <h5 class="mt-4">4. Do we share your information?</h5>
    <p>We do not sell your information. We may share some data with trusted third parties to provide our service:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>WhatsApp Business API or its provider (e.g., Twilio).</li>
        <li>Web analytics platforms (e.g., Google Analytics).</li>
        <li>Payment services (e.g., PayPal, if you use a premium plan).</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These third parties are required to protect your information and not use it for other purposes.</p>

    <h5 class="mt-4">5. Cookies and similar technologies</h5>
    <p>We use cookies to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Save your preferences.</li>
        <li>Analyze website usage and improve performance.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can configure your browser to block cookies, but this may affect the site's functionality.</p>

    <h5 class="mt-4">6. Data security</h5>
    <p>We implement security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, loss, or destruction.</p>

    <h5 class="mt-4">7. Your rights</h5>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data.</li>
        <li>Correct or update your information.</li>
        <li>Request the deletion of your account and data.</li>
        <li>Object to the use of your data for marketing purposes.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at: 📧 <a href="notiksup@gmail.com">notiksup@gmail.com</a></p>

    <h5 class="mt-4">8. Changes to this policy</h5>
    <p>We may update this policy. We will notify you of relevant changes via email or on the website.</p>

    <p class="mt-4">Thank you for trusting NotiK.</p>
